:

1. On je lako* kupio novi auto. (He easily bought a new car.)
2. Lako* ćeš naći put do škole. (You will easily find the way to school.)
3. Nije lako* postati uspešan. (It is not easy to become successful.)
4. Ona je lakše* odgovorila na pitanje. (She answered the question more easily.)
5. Lako* ću se prebaciti na novi posao. (I will easily transfer to a new job.)
6. To je bilo lakše* nego što sam očekivao. (It was easier than I expected.)